          'Bought new domain <a href="https://cworld0.com/" target="_blank">cworld0.com</a> with new redesigned theme <a href="https://github.com/cworld1/astro-theme-pure" target="_blank">Astro Theme Pure</a>'
      }
    ]}
  />
