    <li>
      Visits: <a href='https://console.leancloud.app/' target='_blank'>LeanCloud</a> +
      <a href='https://waline.js.org/' target='_blank'>Waline</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      Other statistics: <a href='https://github.com/spencerwooo/substats' target='_blank'
        >Substats</a
      > & <a href='https://github.com/Rock-Candy-Tea/hexo-circle-of-friends' target='_blank'
        >Circle of friends</a
      >
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p>... and one thing I have been insisting on so far:</p>
  <a href='https://notbyai.fyi/' target='_blank'>
    <Image
      src={notByAIImage}
      alt='Written by Human Not by AI'
      width='131'
      height='42'
      style='border-radius:unset'
    />
  </a>
  <Comment slot='bottom' />
</PageLayout>
